			Hi, I’m Chen Zhao, a Research Scientist at QuEra Computing Inc. in Boston, MA. My research interests include quantum error correction, quantum algorithms, and quantum software. I enjoy exploring and verifying my research ideas through coding, primarily using Julia and Python, which allows me to seamlessly translate theory into practice. 
		</p>
		<p>
			Outside of my research work, I am also a professional yo-yoer, combining precision and creativity in a completely different field. Check out <a href="https://www.instagram.com/zhao_chen/" target="_blank">my Instagram</a> to see more about my life beyond the lab.
		</p>
